11-12 July - Italian Spice Cookie (meatball)

- 6     cup flour
- 2 1/4 cup sugar
- 1 1/4 cup crisco
- 3 1/2 teaspoon baking powder
- 2 1/2 teaspoon cinnamon
- 2 1/2 teaspoon cloves
- 1/2   teaspoon pepper
- 1     teaspoon allspice
- 8     eggs
- 1 1/2 teaspoon vanilla
- 1     cup walnuts
- 6     chocolate squares, melted

Mix dry ingredients, add Crisco. When mixed, make a well and add eggs a little at a time. add vanilla, chocolate squares and walnuts. Bake in a preheated 375F oven on a greased cookie sheet about 10 minutes. Cover with icing when cooled. 